// tryRotate — silent sound objects rewrite
// Original: -gr.tryRotate (Bernard, 1998)
// _rotate = engine control (structural)
RND
gram#1[1] S --> /6  {_rotate(K1=2) M} 1/2 N
gram#1[2] <5-1> N --> N _rotate(K1) {N 1/2}
-----------
RND
gram#2[1] M --> C4 D4 E4 F4 G4
gram#2[2] N --> C5 D5 E5 F5 G5 A5 B5 C6 D6 E6
